#' Internal function to create the dictionaries
#' This script contains a separate function called generate_dictionary_script. This can be used to read in a modified dictionary and will then give out the code to insert into this function.
#' @param single_df Logical. If TRUE, the function will return a single data frame with all dictionaries. If FALSE, the function will return a list of data frames.
#'
#' @returns Either a list of dictionaries or a data.frame with a single dictionary.
